description: Silver Elephant Mining Corp., a mineral exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral and energy projects. The company explores for gold, nickel, silver, lead, zinc, iron, vanadium, titanium, and coal. Its flagship project is the Pulacayo project, including seven mining areas covering an area of approximately 3,560 hectares of contiguous areas located in Quijarro province, Bolivia. The company was formerly known as Prophecy Development Corp. and changed its name to Silver Elephant Mining Corp. in March 2020. Silver Elephant Mining Corp. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. John R.  Lee BCom, BEdpg, C.F.A., CFA, FAICD, MBA, SAFin
